{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bg":"black","nameNarration":"","narration":"―Epilogue―","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":37.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_11141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story08","chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"...It's really great that you were discharged.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Thank you very much..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"You haven't fully recovered yet, right?@Don't push yourself."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":304301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Eternal Sakura","textRight":"| So, your number of interview records have@increased? |"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes, with the help of everyone from Puella Care..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Take a look at some of these..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"white","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:―Interview Record―@Perenelle Flamel]","narrationBg":"white","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_11141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Wh...WHAT?!","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Aru","textLeft":"<Kagome! Stay calm! Stay calm!>"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"What's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":304301,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Eternal Sakura","textRight":"| Are you getting agitated from reading the@interview records? |"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Aru","textLeft":"<Miss Melissa, Miss Elisa, Miss Liz...>"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Aru","textLeft":"<There are lots of names of Magical Girls we don't@know.>"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"(There's one name I know, but she's not an@\"acquaintance\"!)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"(Jeanne d'Arc...!)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Um...are those the ones that Puella Care wrote?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"But this is my handwriting...?@My handwriting looks like..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_11141.jpg","chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":200}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Click, click*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11141.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"See...it's like this."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100501,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Felicia","textRight":"Yep, that's your handwriting."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":100201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"Oh, that mechanical pencil is cute."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Huh? You think so?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":100201,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"The mascot attached to it is Aru, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Oh... Huh?![chara:102001:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:102001:motion_400][chara:102001:cheek_0][chara:102001:face_mtn_ex_050.exp3.json][chara:102001:lipSynch_1]@EEEEEEEH?!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Aru","textLeft":"<Kagome doesn't seem to have any memories of@buying it.>"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":304301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","visible":"hide"}],"nameRight":"Eternal Sakura","textRight":"| Kagome, you're acting strange. |"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Have I...lost some memories from before my@hospitalization?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Hey, are you okay?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Ui","textRight":"...This interview record seems really unbelievable,@doesn't it...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Can I...read it a little?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":101501,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Ui","textRight":"Ah, but it's hard to read with everyone here, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"You can take your time reading in that room over@there."},{"chara":[{"id":100201,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"You must be tired from going out after such a long@time."},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"nameRight":"Yachiyo","textRight":"I'll prepare tea and snacks."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","nameNarration":"","narration":"*Knock knock*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Ah...come in..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102001,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"We brought tea and snacks."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101501,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Ui","textRight":"I'll leave them here!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"So...how was it?"},{"chara":[{"id":100101}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Did you learn anything from reading the interview@records?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes, about that..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":201,"pos":2,"posX":30}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Tart","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"Because beyond that,@  there is a world where@  everyone can live in peace...@  I believe there is hope.\"]","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":402101,"motion":0}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:\"I believe in that light...@And keep my gaze forward.\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"If everything written here is true,","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"it would explain why my memories are missing..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"But..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"But?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"(An interview record about Jeanne d'Arc...!)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Um...I don't think I can make anyone believe it..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Aru","textLeft":"<It seems Kagome herself can't believe it.>"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Ahaha...well, there's nothing we can do about that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"If you ever feel like talking about it, just let us know."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...Thank you very much."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"But I have a hunch that the feelings of all the@different people written here..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"They're probably real..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100101,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Hehehe."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100401,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"...By the way, Kagome, speaking of your@Magical Girl interview records..."},{"chara":[{"id":100401}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"They're starting to pile up quite a bit."},{"chara":[{"id":100401}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Are you not going to give them a name?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101501,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Ui","textLeft":"Like the title of a book...?"},{"chara":[{"id":100401,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Sana","textRight":"Yes...I'm a little curious."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"A name? Well...I have been thinking about it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Oh, can we hear it?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I'm thinking of calling it \"[textRed:Magia Record]\"."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"La Fin.@(The End.)","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":37.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.5},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
